_IMAGING_HELLO_

_MASK_BAD_PIXELS_
_SUBTRACT_DARK_
_NORMALISE_SINGLE_FRAME_
_FILE_FLAT_

=head1 NAME

REDUCE_FLAT - Reduces an imaging Flat Field

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Reduces a flat field in the conventional manner, including
normalisation by the mean of the image. Files the normalised
flat field frame for use by subsequent flat fielding operations.

=head1 AUTHORS

Brad Cavanagh (JAC)

